title: Graduation
body: Well, there it is. The final day at high school is over. Congratulations everyone who graduated and thank you Riot for making league. I've been playing since season 3 and its kept me entertained and distracted me from school work for years. ty rito <3

replies.body:
The real world now awaits you... 

nvm.. league is still here.
I think I made it to year 12 I'm not sure I'm not that smart.
